(48, 1, '2016-04-12 16:30:34', '2016-04-12 16:30:34', '<strong>What does he do?</strong>John is the creator, founder, and owner of SICKY\r\n\r\n<strong>Whats his deal? </strong>In a nutshell, the SICKY brand evolved out of Johns passion to create and learn, his experiences, and his day-to-day life. Well go on the record here, and chock it up to the fact that if it werent for John, SICKYwouldnt exist SICKY is, after-all, his nickname.\r\n\r\nJohn learned to be outgoing and leave it all out on the table at a young age. Subcultural and Art were guiding forces that shaped his outlook on life, and would come in handy as his careers in photography and production evolved. Well-rounded in terms of travel and artistic expression, with a animated punk-rock attitude, John is the linchpin when it comes to bringing groups of talented people together and executing projects that would give a normal person a stroke. Funny too, when we asked him to describe a normal day in his life, John laughed. He paused for a moment. And then he smiled with a hint of bewilderment, and responded, A normal day? Um. There is no normal day. I dont even know what that word means. Every single day is a different adventure. We couldnt have said it better ourselves.\r\n\r\nJohn attended the Brooks Institute for photography, and ran a successful photography studio for over 10 years. He also co-owned and operated an event production company based in Malibu for 13 years, working hand-in-hand with several venues in LA and celebrity clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>What is SICKY?</strong>To me, SICKY means freedom of expression. No barriers. No worries. SICKY, to me means, uh, oh my gosh... it means aggression. It means passion. It means hard work. It means full-of-life. SICKY consumes me to no end. I live and breathe it. SICKY means being proud of who you are - owning it. SICKY is being proud of your individuality and who you are as a person. You stand strong to what you believe in. You back what you say. Again, we couldnt have said it better ourselves.\r\n\r\n<strong>Instagram:<a href="http://instagram.com/johnhildebrandsicky" target="_blank"></a></strong><a href="http://instagram.com/johnhildebrandsicky" target="_blank"><strong>@johnhildebrandsicky</strong></a><strong> Twitter: <a href="http://twitter.com/sickysworld" target="_blank">@sickysworld</a> </strong><strong>Photography Site: <a href="http://www.johnhildebrand.com/" target="_blank">johnhildebrand.com</a></strong><a href="http://twitter.com/sickysworld" target="_blank"><strong></strong></a>', 'John Hildebrand', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'john-hildebrand', '', '', '2016-04-12 16:30:34', '2016-04-12 16:30:34', '', 0, 'http://sickysworld.local/?post_type=crew&#038;p=48', 0, 'crew', '', 0),
