(60, 1, '2016-04-12 19:00:15', '2016-04-12 19:00:15', ' Midnight Black\r\n\r\n Gloss Finish with Gold Metal Brow Bar and Bridge\r\n\r\n Grey Lenses\r\n\r\n Gold plated SICKY logo on temple tips\r\n\r\n Unisex Frame\r\n\r\n Designed in Malibu. Handcrafted in Japan.\r\n\r\n Size and Fit: Eye 51 / Bridge 23 / Temple 145 (in mm)', 'Dean // Black', 'Introducing, DEAN.The original rebel without a cause, James DEAN. The cultural icon that truly embodies the SICKY creative spirit whose infamous stardom has transcended generations. Noted to spend more than a few Summer days laying out on the beaches of SICKYs birthplace, Malibu, this unisex double bar accented frame has an air of cool sophistication impossible to replicate. In our eyes, DEAN is the supreme statement of SICKY Summer style.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dean-black', '', '', '2016-04-13 20:48:52', '2016-04-13 20:48:52', '', 0, 'http://sickysworld.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=60', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2016-04-13 07:47:16', '2016-04-13 07:47:16', '<strong>What does he do? </strong>Cisco is our Creative Director &amp; Chief Branding Officer. Hes our expert when it comes to breakthrough artists, legendary collaborations, and musical genius.\r\n\r\nCollaboration is the name of this game - he has millions of records and 100s of millions of impressions under his belt. With musical capabilities that span almost every genre on the planet, his roster includes legends and up-and-comers alike. In true SICKY fashion, Cisco loves to conncet the dots between the lifestyles of like-minded musicians, entertainers, and world-changers with the same lifestyle that we endorse over here at SICKY.\r\n\r\n<strong>Whats his deal?  </strong>His sun-kissed, beach party tunes pretty much say it all for him! Growing up in between Hawaii and Malibu, Cisco was a product of his environment. He explains that music, his art, his inspiration, and his outlook on life sounds like a beach. He has supplied a distinct reggae-island-rock n roll-esque groove for many-a-gatherin from California to Catalonia, and has collaborated with chart toppers from the likes of Mike Posner, to our favorite party animals like Mickey Avalon and Dirt Nasty. When hes not writing and producing, Cisco is calling the shots at Bananabeat Records, where he is the founder and CEO. Bananabeat is a cultural lifestyle collective dedicated to finding and cultivating talent, technology, and content. As Ciscos musical instincts are just that - instinctual, indicating that it just comes naturally to him - he has developed a knack for finding and facilitating global awareness for new artists. He says, I like to let artists bake until theyre perfectly baked. Welcome to the future... this is what it sounds like. We are listening.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cisco, walk us through a day-in-the-life. </strong>Wake up around 6 or 7 am. Hit the studio til the world wakes up. Get inspired by something or someone, and run off on a tangent trying to create something that will stand the test of time... all the while not taking<strong>anything</strong>too seriously. After all... its only rock and roll. Eat some healthy food. Give my lady some kisses. Handle some business and close some deals. Hit the studio as the sun goes down and make some more music... Some where in between I stop to enjoy the beautiful view. You should too.\r\n\r\n<strong>What does SICKY mean? </strong>Amazing. Unbelievable. Incredible. Outside the norm. Its all at once a slang term along the lines of radical and awesome and also a mantra to live by. Go big. Get SICKY.\r\n\r\n<strong>Twitter:</strong><strong></strong><a href="http://twitter.com/mrciscoadler" target="_blank">@MrCiscoAdler</a><strong>Instagram:</strong><a href="http://instagram.com/ciscoadler" target="_blank"><strong>@</strong>ciscoadler</a><strong></strong>', 'Cisco Adler', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cisco-adler', '', '', '2016-04-16 16:03:15', '2016-04-16 16:03:15', '', 0, 'http://sickysworld.local/?post_type=sicky-crew&#038;p=61', 1, 'sicky-crew', '', 0),
