(64, 1, '2016-04-13 20:30:40', '2016-04-13 20:30:40', '<strong>Online Purchases:</strong> Purchases made online are available for a full refund if not satisfy with the product. Refunds will be credited back to the original purchasers credit card. Any shipping charges paid by customer will be fully refunded. You will have 7 days to refund product if needed. Unless the sunglasses break we will fully cover it up to 1 year of purchase.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Exchange Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Return within 7 days of purchase\r\n\r\n- Item has been unworn\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth are returned\r\n\r\n- Item is free of any damage caused by the customer\r\n\r\n- Item is returned in all original packaging\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Incorrect Item Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- If we sent you the incorrect item we will refund all shipping/handling costs\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth need to be returned\r\n\r\n- Item is free of any damage caused by the customer\r\n\r\n- Items need to be returned in all original packaging\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Defective Item Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- If item was sent defective, you must notify us within 7 days of the purchase date\r\n\r\n- Items need to be returned in all original packaging\r\n\r\n- Any damage claim made after 7 days will not be accepted\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Unsatisfied with Item: </strong>If you are completely unsatisfied with your item, you have the option to return the item within 7 business days of original purchase, as long as all items in the original packaging are included and you provide us with a valid explanation of your need to return.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Try It On:</strong>\r\n\r\nOur "TRY IT ON" policy allows you to feel and try it on for size. SICKY Eyewear backs it''s product 100% and know you will love it. In the case it doesn''t fit your needs, you can fully REFUND the eyewear and SICKY will pay for the the return shipping. You will have up to 7 days of purchase date.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Refund Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Return within 7 days of purchase\r\n\r\n- Item has been unworn\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth are returned\r\n\r\n- Item is free of any damage caused by the customer\r\n\r\n- Item is returned in all original packaging\r\n\r\n- Purchaser provides a signed letter of explanation for their return\r\n\r\n<strong>International Buyers &amp; Shipping</strong>\r\n\r\n- We do not refund costs incurred in international shipping costs on returns at this time\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Retail Purchases:</strong> If you have purchased SICKY product through an authorized dealer, please refer to the dealers return policy and adhere to those terms. If SICKY product falls under Warranty, you have 2 options:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Warranty Inspection Through Retailer:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Contact retailer, provide proof of purchase, and show defective product.\r\n\r\n- Retailer will send product to SICKY for Warranty Approval\r\n\r\n<strong>- Your warranty is valid only if the following criteria are met:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Proof of Purchase is provided from authorized dealer or SICKY Online Store\r\n\r\n- Items need to be returned in all original packaging, including sunglass, case, and cloth are returned\r\n\r\n- Damages are caused by manufacturing defects in production, materials, or workmanship\r\n\r\n<strong>- Your warranty is not valid provided the following criteria:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Normal wear-and-tear does not constitute a valid warranty, including:\r\n\r\n- Scratched or broken lenses\r\n\r\n- Broken arms\r\n\r\n- Lost screws\r\n\r\n- Scratched frames\r\n\r\n- Peeled frames\r\n\r\n- Faded frames\r\n\r\n- Nose piece deterioration\r\n\r\n- Frame deterioration\r\n\r\n- Alteration of frames, accessories, or materials\r\n\r\n- Misuse\r\n\r\n- Abuse\r\n\r\n- Installation of new lenses\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Warranty Inspection Through SICKY:</strong