e?</strong>\r\n\r\nAbsolutely. We value your privacy. Secure Socket Layer (SSL) encryption is used for every transaction, ensuring your security.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>What is your return policy?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Online Purchases:</strong> Purchases made online are available for refunds only. Exchanges are not permitted. Refunds will be credited back to the original purchasers credit card. Any shipping charges paid by customer will not be refunded unless you were shipped a faulty item. SICKY will refund any shipping costs if we are found at fauly for sending a faulty or damaged item.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Refund Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Return within 15 days of purchase\r\n\r\n- Item has been unworn\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth are returned\r\n\r\n- Item is free of any damage caused by the customer\r\n\r\n- Item is returned in its original package\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Incorrect Item Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- If we sent you the incorrect item we will refund all shipping/handling costs\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth need to be returned\r\n\r\n- Item is free of any damage caused by the customer\r\n\r\n- Items need to be returned in original packaging\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Defective Item Terms:</strong>\r\n\r\n- If item was sent defective, you must notify us within 7 days of the purchase date\r\n\r\n- All items, including sunglass, case, and cloth need to be returned\r\n\r\n- Any damage claim made after 7 days will not be accepted\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>International Buyers &amp; Shipping</strong>\r\n\r\n- We do not refund costs incurred in international shipping costs on returns at this time\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Where do I ship my return?</strong>\r\n\r\nSICKY\r\n\r\nc/oRETURNS\r\n\r\nP.O. Box 6161\r\n\r\nScottsdale, AZ 85261\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How should I ship my return?</strong>\r\n\r\nPackage and seal your box securely in its original box and hard case with all accessories included. Use a service that tracks your package to ensure delivery. We do not accept return packages that are not pre-paid.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>When will my credit card be refunded?</strong>\r\n\r\nOnce your package is received, your return will be evaluated and processed within 5-7 business days. If there is a refund due it will be issued in the original form of payment. The refund may not show up until the next months billing cycle. You will be notified via email when the refund transaction has been full', 'Shipping Info', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '68-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-13 20:31:42', '2016-04-13 20:31:42', '', 68, 'http://sickysworld.local/68-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
