(101, 1, '2016-04-14 19:18:33', '2016-04-14 19:18:33', '<h2><strong>OUR STORY</strong></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.sickysworld.com/john-hildebrand">John Hildebrand</a> first began to explore the world through the lens of a camera. The camera became more than a window to the world but a vehicle to identify his artistic point of view and establish a creative vision. When it came time to purchase eyewear, John felt disconnected from the brands on the shelves as they were not as inspiring as the lens that shaped his world. With the same fearless spirit that he approached his art, John set to work in his Malibu garage to create an eyewear brand that he could identify with. Using his nickname <strong>SICKY</strong>, John created prototypes that were bold, distinctive and captured the attention of everyone he met. After attending a party in Malibu, the frames quickly became the center of attention. Everyone wanted to get their own pair of <strong>SICKY</strong>s, a brand that was only in its infancy.\r\n\r\nIn the Summer of 2015 <strong>SICKY</strong> moved full production to the luxury eyewear capital of the world, Japan, and under the new mentorship of a seasoned eyewear expert <strong>SICKY</strong> has continued to be on the cutting edge of quality and design innovation.\r\n\r\n<strong>SICKY</strong> offers a sense of belonging as John looks to the next generation who may find themselves feeling like he did a decade ago. Our story continues with every individual who joins the SICKY movement eager to see the world through a different lens. Now two years later, <strong>SICKYs</strong> has become a movement lead by tastemakers in art, music and popular culture.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>ABOUT SICKY CREW</strong></h2>\r\nThe foundation of <strong>SICKY</strong>s starts with our Crew. An elite hand-picked brand ambassadors that include Songwriters, photographers, painters, writers and musicians. These luminaries chose to align themselves with <strong>SICKY</strong>. While each member of the Crew has a different perspective, they all prefer to see the world through a different lens.\r\n\r\nWe dont punch time cards\r\n\r\nWere the last ones to leave the party and up before the sunrise\r\n\r\nWe work hard to play harder\r\n\r\nSee our crew: <a href="http://www.sickysworld.com/sicky-crew/" target="_blank"><em>www.sickysworld.com/sicky-crew/</em></a>', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-14 19:18:33', '2016-04-14 19:18:33', '', 25, 'http://sickysworld.local/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
